Figure 12. 
<taxonomicName id="42C808585C1597476E60CF2DAAD5813E" genus="A." lsidName="A. piptatheri" pageId="0" pageNumber="15" rank="species" species="piptatheri">A. piptatheri</taxonomicName>
A colony on 
