conidiogenous cells giving rise to conidia. Scale bars: 5 
<normalizedToken id="EE3AA81853A17F55D0BBFE64B3CC479F" originalValue="µm">µm</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="F08AFA41553863F532D427EE20D05BB8" originalValue="B–K">B-K</normalizedToken>
).
</paragraph>
